{"tid":383174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好享受緊張到腳震嗰種感覺？","createTime":"2017-09-01T09:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T14:52:29.000Z","uid":90520,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96f77640fb29e4016ab0ef60a6780cd7636ea26c","tid":383174,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"我就係呢種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面對人群嗰種緊張感 真係正到痴線<br />\n好似之前仲係中學嗰陣 要上台演講<br />\n明知班契弟都唔會聽<br />\n上到台都震到仆街<br />\n不過講嗰陣又係流利冇lag到架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又好似之前sing con唱歌<br />\n一路唱 唱到手都fing黎fing去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腳當然都震到仆咗街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過又唱出個水準來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兩單野 完咗之後 同返啲觀眾吹水<br />\n佢地都見到我腳震到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證明真係震得好誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁搞我都唔知自己算唔算m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416730714de79d6263c8f93dbc40883109608b16","tid":383174,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"緊張係代表你準備狩獵 身體一蓄即發<br />\n我都好享受哩一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb4e6349f66eb85ef0f2c2fb8566409baaac4cb","tid":383174,"uid":54344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"啲腎上腺素標出黎嗰下先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到血管賁張，個心大大力bump啲血